{"lastModified":1761140180057,"uri":"c::33048560166::vessel::ec94e630-36e4-11f0-a2ee-4da53da634f9","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nTHE STORY OF FERRETI 52\n\nOur yacht is a luxury Ferretti Altura 52s flybridge with full amenities. Sea fun guaranteed! She has a total of 4 cabins and 3 bathrooms and can easily accommodate 6 people plus 2 crew.\n\nIt is fully refitted in 2022. Also it has a tender zodiac 3,8m with a 30hp engine. Cruising the Greek islands on our yacht is undoubtedly one of the finest experiences the world has to offer. We are Aegean sea experts and can safely take you to great places, either cosmopolitan islands such as Mykonos or quiet places with fantastic crystal clear waters for swimming and snorkeling, and picturesque island harbours to spend the night, depending on your tastes and preferences.\n\nIt provides every luxury required for an exquisite experience at sea.","blueprint":{"name":"BLUE DREAM","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::ec94e630-36e4-11f0-a2ee-4da53da634f9::assets::f59c4590-36e7-11f0-9781-732fb3434464/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::ec94e630-36e4-11f0-a2ee-4da53da634f9::assets::f59bf770-36e7-11f0-9781-732fb3434464/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::ec94e630-36e4-11f0-a2ee-4da53da634f9::assets::f59cbac0-36e7-11f0-9781-732fb3434464/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::ec94e630-36e4-11f0-a2ee-4da53da634f9::assets::f59cbac1-36e7-11f0-9781-732fb3434464/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::ec94e630-36e4-11f0-a2ee-4da53da634f9::assets::f59a70d0-36e7-11f0-9781-732fb3434464/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::ec94e630-36e4-11f0-a2ee-4da53da634f9::assets::f59bd060-36e7-11f0-9781-732fb3434464/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::ec94e630-36e4-11f0-a2ee-4da53da634f9::assets::f59e8f80-36e7-11f0-9781-732fb3434464/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::ec94e630-36e4-11f0-a2ee-4da53da634f9::assets::f59c93b0-36e7-11f0-9781-